\begin_inset Formula $\pi_{d}<0$
\end_inset

) ...
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
may look ineffective (if 
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha+\pi_{d}\leq0$
\end_inset

)
\end_layout

\end_deeper
